name: Untitled (itch) (0011)
description: This is a simple platformer. You have point A where you start and you have point B where you need to get to. Rules are simple - you can move, run and jump. You are able to move any direction you want and choose the best way to get to the B. The other side of your freedom - you can't turn back. Every time you jump off the platform it disappearing. Be attentive and build your path carefully.
